<div id="registrations">
  <div class="container">
  <div class="row" id="registrations-new" >
    <div class="col-6 left-content">
      <h1> Sign Up </h1>
      <p>当サイトはBand Man同士で新たな繋がり、新たな価値を創出お手伝い致します。</br>
       LIVEを開催したい、新たな地域でまだ知らぬバンドマンと出会いたい</br>
      さあ、あなたもBandをGatherしよう！！　⇒　Sign in。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-6 right-content">
      <%= form_for(resource, as: resource_name, url: registration_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>
        <%= render "users/shared/error_messages", resource: resource %>

        <div class="form-group">
          <%= f.label :user_name, class: "control-label" %><br />
          <%= f.text_field :user_name, autofocus: true, class: "form-control" %>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <%= f.fields_for :band do |f| %>
            <%= f.label :band_name, class: "control-label" %><br />
            <%= f.text_field :band_name, autofocus: true, class: "form-control"  %>
          <% end %>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <%= f.label :email, class: "control-label" %><br />
          <%= f.email_field :email, autofocus: true, autocomplete: "email", class: "form-control"  %>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <%= f.label :password, class: "control-label" %>
          <% if @minimum_password_length %>
          <em>(<%= @minimum_password_length %> characters minimum)</em>
          <% end %><br />
          <%= f.password_field :password, autocomplete: "new-password", class: "form-control"  %>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <%= f.label :password_confirmation, class: "control-label" %><br />
          <%= f.password_field :password_confirmation, autocomplete: "new-password", class: "form-control"  %>
        </div>

        <div class="actions">
          <%= f.submit "Sign up", class: "btn btn-primary" %>
        </div>

        <%= render "users/shared/links",class: "text-right"%>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
  </div>
</div>